OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1783774107
OL,3,CSnake rescued after hiding in police
OL,4,Ccar
OL,6,FGosport Police and the community in
OL,7,FGosport have rescued a snake that had
OL,8,Fslithered into the wheel arch of a
OL,9,Fpolice car.
OL,11,FAt around 1pm today, a police officer
OL,12,Fstopped at a shop on Forton Road when
OL,13,Fhe saw "a very large snake slithering
OL,14,Facross the road" directly in front of
OL,15,Fhim.
OL,17,FPC Biggs says: "On my way back to the
OL,18,Fstation I briefly stopped at Tesco
OL,19,FExpress on Forton Road.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1783774107
OL,3,CSnake rescued after hiding in police
OL,4,Ccar
OL,6,F"As I was driving out of the car park,
OL,7,FI saw what I can only describe as a
OL,8,Fvery large snake slithering across the
OL,9,Froad directly in front of me.
OL,11,F"I immediately jumped out of the
OL,12,Fpolice car and stopped another vehicle
OL,13,Ffrom entering the car park, preventing
OL,14,Fit from running the snake over."
OL,16,FThe police officer describes himself
OL,17,Fas not a snake person and says he has
OL,18,Fno idea how to handle snakes.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1783774107
OL,3,CSnake rescued after hiding in police
OL,4,Ccar
OL,6,FHe continues: "The snake completely
OL,7,Fignored my enthusiastic arm waving and
OL,8,Fcontinued slithering across the car
OL,9,Fpark towards the police car. As I
OL,10,Fwatched, the snake disappeared
OL,11,Funderneath the car."
OL,13,FThe corn snake then climbed into the
OL,14,Fwheel arch and within seconds wrapped
OL,15,Fitself around part of the
OL,16,Fundercarriage.
OL,18,FPC Biggs says "fate intervened"
OL,19,Fbecause a man who owned a reptile shop
OL,20,Fwalked past and helped.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1783774107
OL,3,CSnake rescued after hiding in police
OL,4,Ccar
OL,6,FA local garage also helped and lent
OL,7,Fthe police officer a car jack to raise
OL,8,Fthe vehicle.
OL,10,FAnother member of the community
OL,11,Farrived with a dead mouse to tempt the
OL,12,Fsnake out.
OL,14,FHe continues: "Everyone seemed
OL,15,Fdetermined to help rescue our
OL,16,Funexpected passenger."
OL,18,F"Unfortunately, the more we attempted
OL,19,Fto reach the snake, the deeper it
OL,20,Fwedged itself into the undercarriage.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1783774107
OL,3,CSnake rescued after hiding in police
OL,4,Ccar
OL,6,F"A quick call to Boarhunt provided
OL,7,Fadditional assistance, allowing us to
OL,8,Flift the vehicle even higher."
OL,10,FThe front wheel had to come off along
OL,11,Fwith several other car parts. But
OL,12,Fafter some cable ties were added, the
OL,13,Fsnake was successfully extracted.
OL,15,FThe snake has been taken to a vet for
OL,16,Fa check-up and suffered no injuries.
OL,18,FThe reptile is now being looked after
OL,19,Fat a local reptile centre, and police
OL,20,Fare asking who owns the snake to get
OL,21,Fin touch.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
